			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "- Use debug book to reach SCL (Go to Region -> Act 2 -> SCL -> Mountain Pass).\r\n- Speak to the goblin that warns you about the curse, take a torch, and head down the path. \r\n- The goblin camp is to your south/left.\r\n- Speak to the goblin at the checkpoint.\r\n- Then enter the camp and speak to Kansiff on the wooden platform."
				},
